**WorkHive** is an exclusive bidding platform designed for company associates to compete for job opportunities posted by the admin company. It streamlines the bidding process, allowing associates to view available projects, submit competitive bids, and secure work based on their expertise and proposed costs. The app ensures a fair and transparent system where only verified associates can participate, fostering healthy competition and efficiency. With real-time notifications, bid tracking, and secure approvals, WorkHive simplifies work allocation, ensuring that the right jobs go to the best-suited associates. The platform enhances productivity by enabling seamless communication, efficient job distribution, and structured project execution.
